surface of the Globe. -
Assuming an elevation of temperature
of only 160 degrees where the Ocean
was elevated into the tides which in
it self would not be destructive to life
There is great reason to suppose that
the solvent agency of the water
would be sufficiently increased to

[page]61|MS-DAVY-11702-000-00061|dnp17b59pp|94919281[/page]
enable it to contain with the different
