The water of the ocean in rushing
over the different parts of the land
would necessarliy carry with them
their living inhabitants and many
of their substances forming their
bed. -

[page]62|MS-DAVY-11702-000-00062|dnp17b60pp|94919282[/page]
Where forests were overwhelmed layers
