What ever may be the cause assigned
for this great event it must be
considered as one independent of the
common order of Nature, for in
the usual changes of the Sea and
The and the agencies of the land
nothing analogous occurs and it
must be referred to some power operating
in a novel manner in our Systems
As yet we are not perfectly able
to explain the existing oeconomy

[page]65|MS-DAVY-11702-000-00065|dnp17b63pp|94919285[/page]
