with a calm understanding - -
The strength and the [deletion]corectness[/deletion]
correctness of the imagination can
only be preserved by exercise and
suppositions when they are made only
the amusements of the imagination
are rather useful than injurious
for they increase the activity
the mind the accustom it to rapid
combinations and they are only
dangerous when they are insulated
